How to handle:
Extract the files in the zip archive to a location of your desire. Run fceu.exe. From the menu, choose file-&gt;open and select the game you want to play. Choose config-&gt;input from the menu to set the controls. By default, the arrow keys on the keyboard are used as well as &quot;ctrl&quot; (button B), &quot;alt&quot; (button A), &quot;tab&quot; (select button) and &quot;return&quot; (start button). I&amp;#039;d recommend to use an external keypad instead. Hold down &quot;alt&quot; and press &quot;return&quot; to switch between windowed and fullscreen mode. Have fun.
